data.description: $3,000 CLOSING CREDIT TO BUYER for this meticulously maintained & much admired home in historic Westford center district!  Great curb appeal from expansive front lawn adorned with mature landscaping. 2-story foyer with turned staircase & wrap around balcony.  Kitchen updated with granite, stainless steel, glass tile backsplash, new tile floor & lighting.  Gas line in place to convert appliances if desired.  Family room with soaring cathedral ceiling adjacent to heated sunroom & door to large deck ~ perfect entertaining flow!  1st floor suite is perfect for in-law or master BR.  New hardwood floors in front-to-back living room, dining room & office.  French doors, pocket doors, oversized Anderson windows, 8 ft ceilings on both levels, intercom system, security system, updated roof, furnace & water heater.  Private backyard with wooded border.  Less than ¼ mile walk to town center: library, community center, tennis court, farmers market & Parish Center for the Arts; less than 1 mile to Route 495, shops & restaurants + short drive to award-winning public schools!   CLICK ON VIRTUAL TOUR LINK TO SEE PANORAMIC VIDEO.  Please contact the listing agent, Robin Flynn of Keller Williams Realty, for any questions at robin.flynn@comcast.net or (cell) 978.257.0677.
